{"tid":1471860,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"德智庫：中國若出動解放軍 歐盟制裁力度有限","createTime":"2019-08-14T11:34:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T11:46:07.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"302de4ff3a15c100ce22d797c68c6559d8b83c97","tid":1471860,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:34:41.000Z","msg":"香港反修例示威引發的警民衝突升級，局勢緊張，北京會否出動解放軍平息事件，成為關注點。德國柏林墨卡托中國研究中心(MERICS)總裁皮克(Frank N. Pieke)認為，即使北京作出這項選擇，西方國家，<span style=\"color: red;\">尤其是歐盟幾乎沒有方法，可強硬制裁中國。</span><br />\n<br />\n德國《每日鏡報》(Der Tagesspiegel)引述皮克的分析指，1984年中國與英國簽訂的《中英聯合聲明》沒有保證香港的自由和自治，取而代之的基本法等於將香港主權交給北京的全國人民代表大會，「西方早已接受香港是中國的一部分」。<br />\n<br />\n鑑於目前中美關係緊張，皮克認為，<span style=\"color: red;\">若中國出動解放軍，美國或會抓住機會譴責中國，甚至對其實施制裁，但歐盟各國對中國的態度不一，不大可能協調出共同立場，最多只會是個別國家提出抗議。</span><br />\n<br />\n德國自由民主黨外交政策發言人薩萊(Bijan Djir-Sarai)表示，香港的局勢「讓人嗅到六四事件的氣味」，中國當局如果武力鎮壓示威，<span style=\"color: red;\">國際社會的反應必須非常明確，不要迴避對中國實施經濟制裁。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e3%80%90%e5%8f%8d%e4%bf%ae%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e8%8b%a5%e5%87%ba%e5%8b%95%e8%a7%a3%e6%94%be%e8%bb%8d-%e5%be%b7%e6%99%ba%e5%ba%ab%ef%bc%9a%e8%a5%bf%e6%96%b9%e5%88%b6%e8%a3%81%e5%8a%9b%e5%ba%a6%e6%9c%89%e9%99%90-184730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e5%258f%258d%25e4%25bf%25ae%25e4%25be%258b%25e3%2580%2591%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e8%258b%25a5%25e5%2587%25ba%25e5%258b%2595%25e8%25a7%25a3%25e6%2594%25be%25e8%25bb%258d-%25e5%25be%25b7%25e6%2599%25ba%25e5%25ba%25ab%25ef%25bc%259a%25e8%25a5%25bf%25e6%2596%25b9%25e5%2588%25b6%25e8%25a3%2581%25e5%258a%259b%25e5%25ba%25a6%25e6%259c%2589%25e9%2599%2590-184730&d=SW1PDOKa3sbtYTDDPfmX3fZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=3cc30a10\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e3%80%90%e5%8f%8d%e4%bf%ae%e4%be%8b%e3%80%91%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e8%8b%a5%e5%87%ba%e5%8b%95%e8%a7%a3%e6%94%be%e8%bb%8d-%e5%be%b7%e6%99%ba%e5%ba%ab%ef%bc%9a%e8%a5%bf%e6%96%b9%e5%88%b6%e8%a3%81%e5%8a%9b%e5%ba%a6%e6%9c%89%e9%99%90-184730</a>"},{"pid":"45770da9d9f81fef5fe91c287ec7a799692d2eb4","tid":1471860,"uid":100760,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:37:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mk9NQAd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmk9NQAd.png&h=3c1e4c46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a8vxhfe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa8vxhfe.png&h=9e5f690c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/193648_5871bdc8a2f329da0da5308082ad10bb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F193648_5871bdc8a2f329da0da5308082ad10bb.png&h=ecc06d08&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f03bdca126326c4d4797db813b777e66920b908","tid":1471860,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:42:23.000Z","msg":"Twitter戰線已開，擊退三毛洗板！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1471725/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1471725/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n幫推post然後10點上Twitter做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1861aa66d425509e5e765127c8433c056f71ff08","tid":1471860,"uid":295218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:45:50.000Z","msg":"我班連登仔，我係鬼都忍唔住岀嚟笑柒你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470387\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470387</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d3ded759bd0a219d5e4e65261b7e8de2bd280488","tid":1471860,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:46:07.000Z","msg":"凍結海外資產，禁飛歐美澳就得"}]}